  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u201d\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u201d  \u0bae\u0bcb\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bbf: \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Passport\" Scam in Kandy: Three Caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three persons have been arrested for defrauding youths who come to obtain foreign passports through the Kandy branch of the Immigration and Emigration Department.",
        "The Kandy Police Headquarters said that one employee of the said office and two others who were involved in fraud ranging from 6,000 to 50,000 rupees by claiming to make arrangements for one-day and normal distribution have been arrested.",
        "As one-day and normal service foreign passports are being distributed through the Kandy office, the suspects are involved in fraud by claiming to deliver the passports to the visitors in advance to obtain them.",
        "For this, investigations revealed that 40,000 to 50,000 was received by the suspects for a day's service.",
        "The suspects were arrested while accepting an advance of Rs 25,000 from a youth who had come to collect passports from Tehiyathakandi.",
        "In this, a youth and an auto driver working in the said Immigration-Emigration Department and a person from Matala have been arrested.",
        "While the suspects were initially caught by a few youths, when the authorities took action to release them without taking any legal action, other youths gathered there protested."
      ],
